  </m:mrow>
</m:math>
</para>
<para id="element-44106">Hence, length has the unit of length,
</para>
<para id="element-44107">
<m:math display="block">
  <m:mrow>
    <m:mo>⇒</m:mo>
    <m:mi>L</m:mi>
