</para>
<para id="element-44108">From the dimensional formula of force, we have : 
</para>
<para id="element-44109">
<m:math display="block">
  <m:mrow>
    <m:mo>[</m:mo>
    <m:mi>F</m:mi>
    <m:mo>]</m:mo>
    <m:mo>=</m:mo>
    <m:mo>[</m:mo>
    <m:mi>M</m:mi>
    <m:mi>L</m:mi>
